# hello-baran demo stack — host port map (FR-005, FR-019).
# Copy to .env to override; defaults are baked into docker-compose.yml.
#
# Notes on the contract:
# - The runtime embeds NATS (see core/runtime/config.go: NATSPort/NATSStoreDir),
#   so we do NOT run a separate `nats` service. The runtime container exposes
#   4222 (NATS clients) and 8222 (NATS monitoring) to the host. This deviates
#   from contracts/compose-services.md (which listed `nats` as its own service);
#   the deviation is documented in specs/018-hello-baran-demo/notes.md.
# - The sidecar default port is 9090 (sidecar/config.go), not 8080 — running
#   it on 8080 would collide with the runtime operator/health API on 8080.

NATS_PORT=4222
NATS_MONITOR_PORT=8222
RUNTIME_HTTP_PORT=8080
SIDECAR_PORT=9090
OPERATOR_UI_PORT=3000
